io.github.utk003.util.data.collection.bijection

Class Bijection.Pairing<A,B>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.utk003.util.data.collection.bijection.Bijection.Pairing<A,B>
  • Type Parameters:
    A - The type of the first element in this bijective mapping
    B - The type of the second element in this bijective mapping
    Enclosing interface:
    Bijection<A,B>

    public static final class Bijection.Pairing<A,B>
extends Object
    A utility class representing a unique 1:1 mapping between two elements in a bijection.

    This class plays a very similar role to what Map.Entry does for Map.

    Since:
    2.0.0
    Version:
    April 23, 2021
    Author:
    Utkarsh Priyam (utk003)
    See Also:
    Map.Entry
